name: MovieApp-Microservices

description: This is a part of Reward Your Teacher Microservice web application that handles the User interface using React

description: This is a part of Reward Your Teacher Microservice web application which handles the Teachers, Students and the user registration etc

description: Multi-Ticket Booking Application using NoSQL, mongoDB where user and hotels have noSQL while relationship established with MySQL in train and bus microservice

description: This is a part of Reward Your Teachers Microservice web application that handles the account creation, payment, withdrawal etc for the students and teachers
